data.description: NO HOA! Come check out this spacious 3 bedroom, 2 bathroom home located in a neighborhood close to all the things! With its split floor plan, neutral color scheme, laminate floors, fenced in backyard, double car garage, vaulted ceilings, bonus space that can be easily converted to a 4th bedroom, and more, you'll be sure to have plenty of space inside and out. This neighborhood is only 15 minutes from Kings Bay Naval Base and 5 minutes from Interstate 95. Call today to schedule your showing!
